            <h2>Republic Airlines Cancellation policy</h2>
            <p>A Republic airway is a regional airline that is headquartered in Indianapolis, Indiana. The airways operate services such as American Eagle, Delta Connection, and United Express. If you have booked flight tickets from republic airways but somehow, you’ll have to cancel the ticket, you can cancel the tickets without any headache. Let’s see understand the cancellation policy of the airlines, to help you with the process. </p>
            <p>According to Republic airways cancellation policy, if you cancel the flight tickets within 24 hours of booking, you will get a complete refund of the booking. However, if you fail to <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/titan-airways-cancellation-policy.aspx">cancel the flight within 24 hours</a>, you will have to pay a cancellation fee depending upon the ticket reservation. The cancellation fee you need to pay after 24 hours is $100 to $500. If you cancel a flight within 24 hours from the scheduled departure of your flight, then you will have to pay a cancellation fee of $100 to $400. </p>
            <p>If the flight gets canceled due to any unavoidable reasons from the airline, the airline will provide you compensation to book the next subsequent Republic Airlines flight. If you aren’t satisfied with the same, you can easily cancel your flight and get a refund from the airline. </p>
            <h2>Refund policy</h2>
            <p>If your flight ticket reservation is refundable, you will get a refund in the original form. In case, the <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/">flight ticket</a> is non-refundable, you will receive the refund in the form of travel cash. Travel cash is you may use the refunded amount in your next travel with Republic airways. </p>
            <h3>Frequently asked question</h3>
            <h3>How to cancel a flight ticket with Republic airways? </h3>
            <p>You can call the Republic airways customer care office and inform them about the cancellation. You may also contact your kiosk to help you through the cancellation process. Apart from this, you may also visit the official website of the airlines and cancel your flight ticket. </p>
            <h3>When can I make the request for the refund? By when can I expect it? </h3>
            <p>You can make a request for a refund by filling out a refund request form on Saudi Arabian Airlines’ official website. The refund request takes time to be processed and can be granted within 7 to 10 working days. </p>
            <h3>Can I ask for compensation if my flight gets delayed by 2 hours? </h3>
            <p>If your replacement flight delays your arrival by 2 or more hours or your flight was canceled less than 14 days before departure, you are eligible to get compensation. </p>
            <h3>How to check if my flight is refundable? </h3>
            <p>You can check if your flight is refundable by visiting the official website of the airline and entering the ticket or document number and Republic Airlines will display refund eligibility and information. </p>
